---
// HorarioControls.astro
---

<section
    class="flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-[#757680]/20 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between"
>
    <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#64748B]">
            Generación de Periodo Académico
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[#757680]">
            Haga clic para iniciar el motor de optimización backend.
        </p>
    </div>
    <button
        id="btn-generar"
        class="transform rounded-xl bg-[#1A5AD7] px-8 py-3 font-semibold text-white shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-[#1A5AD7]/90 hover:shadow-lg active:translate-y-0"
    >
        Generar Horarios
    </button>
</section>
